---
import LearnBtn from "../unitComponents/LearnBtn.astro";
---

<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col my-20 px-8">
  <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">
    <h1>TriasoÂ® 'Total air'</h1>
    <h1 class="text-red-600">Burners</h1>
    <div class="mt-4 mb-6 flex">
      <div class="w-20 h-0.5 bg-red-500"></div>
      <div class="w-20 h-0.5 bg-gray-300"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
    <video
      class="w-4/5 md:w-1/2"
      playsinline
      controls
      poster="/public/Gallery/customdes.webp"
      preload="metadata"
      width="1280"
      height="720"
    >
      <source src="/public/Videos/Webm/burnerVideo.webp" type="video/webm" />
      <source src="/public/Videos/Mp4/burnerVideo.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    </video>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-10">
    <div
      class="font-semibold text-sm md:text-base bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-2xs text-grisPPP"
    >
      <p>
        Our burners regulate <strong class="text-black"
          >100% of the air for combustion</strong
        > without relying on the drum's exhaust system. This ensures total combustion
        and <strong class="text-black">100% fuel utilization</strong>,
        effectively preventing various types of problems.
      </p>
      <ul class="pl-4 pt-4">
        <li class="list-disc">Atmospheric pollution.</li>
        <li class="list-disc">
          Contamination of the asphalt mix with unburned fuel.
        </li>
        <li class="list-disc">
          Clogging in the baghouse and a high risk of fire.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div
      class="font-semibold text-sm md:text-base bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-2xs text-grisPPP"
    >
      <p>
        <strong class="text-black">Low NOx emissions </strong>(nitrogen oxides),
        a greenhouse gas that is highly regulated in most regions. It can be
        equipped with a flame protection system to reduce NOx to levels allowed
        by the authorities in your region.
      </p>
      <ul class="pl-4 pt-4">
        <li class="list-disc">
          Sealed installation, without cold air inlets, saving the fuel used to
          heat it, allowing for precise and efficient carburation.
        </li>
        <li class="list-disc">
          Efficiency is not affected by changes in weather temperature
          throughout the day.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
    <LearnBtn href="/Burners" />
  </div>
</section>
